data.description:
Home For Sale Garden City Mo
Home for sale in Cass County Mo, 3-bedroom, 2 bathrooms built in 1984. Side/Side Split level home located in the city limits of Garden City, this home has so much to offer with a huge fenced in back yard at the end of the road. Very open floor plan as the kitchen overlooks the living room, kitchen is spacious with lots of cabinets and all kitchen appliances do stay with the home. Walkout deck off the kitchen that was just built in 2023. The 3 bedrooms are all upstairs with the master having its own private bath.  Living room has fireplace and wood beams on the vaulted ceiling. Downstairs has a laundry room, lots of storage and a 2-car garage. Sherwood schools, taxes in 2022 approx. $1200, high speed internet at the home. Natural gas furnace and hot water heater.
Home For Sale Cass County Mo
This home sits inside the city limits of Garden City Mo, it’s at the end of the road with open fields for your view. Great neighborhood, growing community and only 15 min to Harrisonville Mo. There is shopping, dining and hospitals all close by. Enjoy living in a small community with all the big city amenities close by. Large, fenced back yard with nice shade trees, a beautiful deck to watch the sunset.
